text: Víctor Samuel Palma César (born 19 January 1957) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Morelos. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:People from Cuernavaca Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
